<title>USA: Informix says CFO Hendricks resigns.</title>
<headline>Informix says CFO Hendricks resigns.</headline>
<dateline>MENLO PARK, Calif 1997-05-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Informix Corp said Thursday chief financial officer Alan Hendricks has resigned and the company has hired Howard Karr &amp; Associates to help search for a replacement.</p>
<p>Hendricks, who had held the post since January, said in the news release that the resignation was a difficult decision.  No reason was given for the move, which is effective immediately.</p>
<p>The company's stock has fallen sharply in recent weeks due to unexpectedly weak first quarter sales.</p>
<p>Informix writes computer programs that let big companies store and retrieve huge amounts of data.</p>
